### Dashboard API Tests

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7081/api/admin/dashboard

### Get Dashboard Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Dashboard Metrics with Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Account Counts
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Account Counts with Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/count?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Account List (Paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Account List with Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&email=test&isActive=true&sortBy=CreatedDate&sortOrder=Descending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Account Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Expert Penalties
GET {{baseUrl}}/experts/penalties?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Expert Penalties with Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/experts/penalties?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&expertName=John&fromDate=2024-01-01&toDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Revenue Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/revenue?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31&groupBy=day
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Revenue Statistics by Week
GET {{baseUrl}}/revenue?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31&groupBy=week
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Revenue Statistics by Month
GET {{baseUrl}}/revenue?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31&groupBy=month
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Test Count Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/tests/count?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31&groupBy=day
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Test Count Statistics by Week
GET {{baseUrl}}/tests/count?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31&groupBy=week
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Test Count Statistics with Test Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/tests/count?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31&groupBy=day&testType=ai
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Penalty Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/penalties/statistics?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31&groupBy=day
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Penalty Statistics by Week
GET {{baseUrl}}/penalties/statistics?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31&groupBy=week
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Expert Activity
GET {{baseUrl}}/experts/activity?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Expert Activity with Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/experts/activity?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&expertName=John&fromDate=2024-01-01&toDate=2024-12-31&sortBy=Date
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}